'ip[1]& 0xfc = 0x00' = CS0 default
'ip[1]& 0xfc = 0x08' = CS1 Scavenger
'ip[1]& 0xfc = 0x10' = CS2 OAM
'ip[1]& 0xfc = 0x18' = CS3 Signaling
'ip[1]& 0xfc = 0x20' = CS4 Realtime
'ip[1]& 0xfc = 0x28' = CS5 Broadcast video
'ip[1]& 0xfc = 0x30' = CS6 Network control
... etc.

'ip[25]& 0xfc = 0x08' = CS1 Scavenger
'ip[25]& 0xfc = 0x10' = CS2 OAM
'ip[25]& 0xfc = 0x18' = CS3 Signaling
'ip[25]& 0xfc = 0x20' = CS4 Realtime
'ip[25]& 0xfc = 0x28' = CS5 Broadcast video
'ip[25]& 0xfc = 0x30' = CS6 Network control
... etc.

'(ip6[0]& 0xff = 0x60 and ip6[1]&0xc0=0)' = CS0 default
'(ip6[0]& 0xff = 0x62 and ip6[1]&0xc0=0)' = CS1 Scavenger
'(ip6[0]& 0xff = 0x64 and ip6[1]&0xc0=0)' = CS2 OAM
'(ip6[0]& 0xff = 0x66 and ip6[1]&0xc0=0)' = CS3 Signaling
'(ip6[0]& 0xff = 0x68 and ip6[1]&0xc0=0)' = CS4 Realtime
'(ip6[0]& 0xff = 0x69 and ip6[1]&0xc0=0)' = CS5 Broadcast video
'(ip6[0]& 0xff = 0x6c and ip6[1]&0xc0=0)' = CS6 Network control
'(ip6[0]& 0xff = 0x6d and ip6[1]&0xc0=0)' = CS7
... etc.

div.div:
Extension headers:
'ip6[6]=0' = Hop-by-Hop Options
'ip6[6]=60' = Destination Options (before routing header)
'ip6[6]=43' = Routing
'ip6[6]=44' = Fragment
'ip6[6]=51' = Authentication Header (AH)
'ip6[6]=50' = Encapsulating Security Payload (ESP)
'ip6[6]=60' = Destination Options (before upper-layer header)
